5. **TypeScript Infrastructure**
   - Path aliases (@/components, @/layouts, @/types, @/scripts, @/styles, @/data)
   - Strict mode enabled
   - SEOMeta interface for layout props
   - Feature domain models (NavLink, FeatureCard, PricingTier, Command, Workflow)

