- **Deployment:** Vercel with Web Analytics
- **Icons:** lucide-astro 0.555.0
- **Fonts:** Space Grotesk, DM Sans, Fira Code (via @fontsource)
- **Interactivity:** Alpine.js 3.15.2 (for tab navigation)

